* Excellent research skills; ability to go search through online libraries and databases to produce original and good quality content and grab the useful material
* Outstanding at meeting tough deadlines
* Good communication and interpersonal skills
* Punctuality and regularity
Note: there is a possibility of hiring in case of reasonable performance during internship.
